<!DOCTYPE html>

<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Projects</title>
    <%- include('../partials/Header') %>
</head>
<body>
    <style>
        .projectContainer {
            border: 2px solid black;
            width: 250px;
            height: 250px;
            background-color: #eee;
            margin-left: 5%;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: top;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: left;
        }

            .projectContainer:hover {
                background-color: #eee;
                cursor: pointer;
                border: 2px solid red;
            }

        .pDescription {
            color: black;
            width: 90%;
            position: relative;
            left: 5%;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .pTitle {
            width: 100%;
            height: 12%;
            background-color: #181818;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 25px;
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0%;
        }

        .previewImg {
            width: 100%;
            height: 88%;
            opacity: 0.6;
            opacity: 1;
            transition: opacity 0.55s ease-in-out;
            -moz-transition: opacity 0.55s ease-in-out;
            -webkit-transition: opacity 0.55s ease-in-out;
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            border-radius: 1%;
        }

        .projectContainer:hover .previewImg {
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.5s ease-in-out;
            -moz-transition: opacity 0.5s ease-in-out;
            -webkit-transition: opacity 0.5s ease-in-out;
        }

        #featured {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #bcf5f2;
            text-align: center
        }

        .featured {
            width: 400px;
        }
    </style>
    <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>
    <div class="w3-row-padding w3-padding-64 w3-container w3-light-grey">
        <h1>Projects</h1>
        <div id="featured">
            <h2 style="text-align: center">Featured:</h2>
            <div class="projectContainer featured">
                <a href="/finance/login">
                    <div class="pTitle">
                        Budget starter
                    </div>
                    <div class="pDescription">
                        This project drove from the same foundations that I built a nodejs project. I wanted another project under my toolbelt that utilized technologies like React, Cloud-based databases, and more
                    </div>
                    <img class="previewImg" src="/img/Budget.jpg" />
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="projectContainer featured">
                <a href="/projects/distance">
                    <div class="pTitle">
                        Distance calculator
                    </div>
                    <div class="pDescription">
                        This project searches state abbreviations using simple graph theory and calculates which depot should ship what, according to fairness and efficiency. This arose from a work meeting and was meant as a prototype.
                    </div>
                    <img class="previewImg" src="/img/Distance.jpg" />
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="projectContainer">
            <a href="/projects/distort">
                <div class="pTitle">
                    Photo distorter
                </div>
                <div class="pDescription">
                    This project arose from a bit of boredom mixed with a bit of creativity! After taking my Computer Graphics course, I became curious into the prospect of manipulating pixels. Thus this mini project was born. Copy and paste an image and apply affects! 
                </div>
                <img class="previewImg" src="/img/PhotoDistort.jpg" />
            </a>
        </div>


        <div class="projectContainer">
            <a href="/projects/game">
                <div class="pTitle">
                    Senior game
                </div>
                <div class="pDescription">
                    I created this little game in my senior year of highschool for a programming class. It's a basic game, but I just used canvas and no external libraries. 
                </div>
                <img class="previewImg" src="/img/SeniorGame.jpg" />
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="projectContainer">
            <a href="/projects/gamble">
                <div class="pTitle">
                    Gambling simulator
                </div>
                <div class="pDescription">
                    This was created after my coworker <i>insisted</i> that he would be able to get lucky by gambling on horse races. I created a simulated environment and ran tests to see how many attempts it would take, and the odds of it happening.
                </div>
                <img class="previewImg" src="/img/Gambling.jpg" />
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="projectContainer">
            <a href="/projects/graph">
                <div class="pTitle">
                    Graphing calculator
                </div>
                <div class="pDescription">
                    This project was created because it was I was on summer break and bored. I just finished calculus 2 and was interested in creating my own graphing calculator.
                </div>
                <img class="previewImg" src="/img/Graph.jpg" />
            </a>
        </div>


    </div>

    <div class="w3-container w3-black w3-center w3-opacity w3-padding-64">
        <h1 class="w3-margin w3-xlarge">Quote of the decade: Strive for being nothing less than love</h1>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
